AN ACT relating to governmental administration; requiring certain
public entities to post certain information relating to
purchasing on their Internet websites; revising the duties
of the Commission to Study Governmental Purchasing;
abolishing the Regional Business Development Advisory
Council for Clark County; eliminating a requirement that
institutions of the Nevada System of Higher Education
provide certain mentoring to certain businesses
participating in the NV Grow Program; and providing
other matters properly relating thereto.
Legislative Counsel’s Digest:
