33 programs and procedures to encourage and promote the use of local businesses
34 owned and operated by disadvantaged persons, particularly in the area of
35 contracting and procurement by public agencies in Clark County. (Sections 15 and
36 20 of chapter 7, Statutes of Nevada 2003, 20th Special Session, at pages 268 and
37 269) Section 15 of this bill abolishes the Regional Business Development Advisory
38 Council for Clark County.
